			<div class="wnd-body">
				<div class="wnd-body-inner"  style="">

Magelo was founded by Christian Meunier, a dedicated gamer, in his college dorm room in 2001. 
Christian (a.k.a Jelan) initially created a system to make Everquest character profiles solely for his guildmates. 
However, the character profiles spread quickly and soon Magelo was born, serving hundreds of thousands of users.
<br><br>
With our deeply personal roots as gaming purists, Magelo seeks to enrich players gaming experience, both in and out of the game, by providing database, character profiling, signature, and social networking tools. 
<br><br>

<div class="WINDOW-BODY-TITLE"><img src="http://www.magelocdn.com/images/website/localized/picto/home_puce_orange.png?v=10895" height="12" alt="" width="12" class="png32" />&nbsp;Thank you!</div>
<br>
This site would not be possible without the suggestions and comments from our users, that help us to going forward. A HUGE thanks to all of you!
Your feedback is important to us in how we can better improve Magelo. 
So feel free to <a href="contact_us.jspa">contact us</a> if you have any suggestions or comments! We are always open to new opportunities as well. 
Thanks also to all the volunteer advisors who keep the wheels turning. 
<br><br>

<div class="WINDOW-BODY-TITLE"><img src="http://www.magelocdn.com/images/website/localized/picto/home_puce_orange.png?v=10895" height="12" alt="" width="12" class="png32" />&nbsp;No Ads! policy</div>
<br>
As you have probably noticed, there are no ads on our website. That's the result of our No Ads! policy. We feel strongly that a gaming community website like ours should focus on just one thing: entertainment! <br><br>
Of course, our No Ads! policy has a cost. We strive to create a safe haven for those who want to rest their minds and take a break from everyday life. All of this wouldn't be possible if it weren't for our Premium subscribers (thank you!). 
If you like our services would like to take them to the next level, please consider upgrading to our Premium Subscription! 
<br><br>
